title: Take a Peek Inside Jennifer Aniston's Modern Bel Air Mansion

meta_data.description:
Jennifer Aniston purchased the property seven years ago for $21 million.
And now Jennifer Aniston has welcomed readers inside the stunning Bel Air estate she shares with her husband Justin Theroux for Architectural Digest magazine.

More...
